1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,560
He’s definitely telling that one story again.

2
00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:03,120
And everyone is pretending it’s new.

3
00:00:03,120 --> 00:00:04,679
The laughter is getting a little too loud.

4
00:00:04,679 --> 00:00:06,240
He leans in to make it even more dramatic.

5
00:00:06,240 --> 00:00:07,799
Somebody please tell him to breathe.

6
00:00:07,799 --> 00:00:09,359
Still laughing, still dramatic, same old story.
